{"featured_counts":5,"common_counts":156,"collapsed_counts":0,"reviewing_counts":0,"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/560685409/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=65\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/560685409/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=63\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","totals":73},"data":[{"id":567507182,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/567507182","content":"我高中也是如此，对一切世俗看不过去，迫切要得到更多荣誉、地位、名气。最近研究仙侠小说，发现这正是所有人的共性，也是所有研究的动力。把推动一个像是数学学科的动力寄托在所谓纯粹的爱科学之心，不仅不现实，反而好笑。我并不认为当今时代还会有完全纯粹的不为任何名利、荣誉动摇做研究的（刨除了确实感兴趣，必然是私心，兴趣也是私心。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e我觉得好笑的，只是这一点，必然有不少科研无无反响的学者，而看着别的追名逐利的人事业蒸蒸日上，必然心理不平衡，也就因此需要一种观念来减缓这种不平衡，这个观念就是信仰，，即是你可以说“我是为着某种找到真理的信仰在度过这些时间，我不追名逐利”。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e我觉得这样的信仰很搞笑，但不得不说又没有别的观念可以使人内心平衡。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e但它有一个缺点，那就是让那些深信不疑的人真的以为可以有摆脱所有名誉利的淡薄研究方式存在，并且尝试装着那样的方式做，竟甚而深以为傲，但却忘记了这种观念存在的初衷。","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1546092821,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"f12d479140500349d9e39880bed2e49e","url_token":"bi-mu-yu-35-24","name":"九天揽月","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3b9a4508eda4139411c2232ab8cb9bdc_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3b9a4508eda4139411c2232ab8cb9bdc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f12d479140500349d9e39880bed2e49e","user_type":"people","headline":"大能之辈","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":0,"voting"